cosi-adventure XMPP Bot
=======================

Dependencies
------------
 * libstrophe
 * cosi-adventure

Notes
-----
bot.c code shamelessly borrowed from http://github.com/metajack/libstrophe/examples/bot.c
Place the cosi-adventure binary, and data file in the same directory as the bot.
Run the bot with ./bot <jid> <pass>, any valid pair will do.

Example:
./bot username@xmpp.server.net password1234
